{"tid":536874,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家珍惜陳展鵬胡定欣","createTime":"2018-01-22T08:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T19:26:28.000Z","uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"76d28fbea17a17ac138699123b627ed219cabf12","tid":536874,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"當唐c wing都做到視后個陣，就知到陳展鵬胡定欣其實好好<br />\n<br />\n其實呢兩條友同林峯一樣，都係因為畀tbb日捧夜捧搞到d人唔中意，但事實上都係有實力嘅<br />\n<br />\n大家仲差林峯一個視帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於胡定欣同陳展鵬，其實畀人捧之前一向都唔差，陳展鵬張保仔個年個個連登仔仲撐佢拎視帝，胡定欣之前做啞妹打拳都好多人支持，佢喵喵星其實唔應該拎，反而城寨拎就差唔多<br />\n<br />\n而家連唐c wing都拎到獎，請大家珍惜陳展鵬胡定欣，唔好好似屌林峯咁屌走埋佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903d335c17f5ab83aaa52819fb0adfe849ddc685","tid":536874,"uid":4709,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"陳展鵬就收收皮先<br />\n陣柒味老套味真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252299484be85f13a4f5cecaa4c1ec99606d67f8","tid":536874,"uid":35870,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳展鵬就收收皮先<br />\n陣柒味老套味真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乘勝狙擊入面好型喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70da9d512875d9d2f9d627ccbec39a498048ae47","tid":536874,"uid":104725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"之前重播張保仔都追住睇"},{"pid":"a2c05106b3afc508230cb8e8ba5ae425d00d6584","tid":536874,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前重播張保仔都追住睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識貨"},{"pid":"2894cab50a12b410668103475bcb9fa28b2d1a3c","tid":536874,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:20:15.000Z","msg